timing_generat...river_waveform(25.10)  timing_generat...river_waveform(25.10)

Name
       timing_generate_normalized_driver_waveform

Syntax
       timing_generate_normalized_driver_waveform

       {0 | 1}

       Default: 1

       Generates  the analytical normalized driver waveform for timing library
       if the waveform is not specified in the library. The waveform is gener-
       ated by weighed mean of linear and exponential waveform.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

